---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About" description="About Jasper Japp">
  <!-- Page heading -->
  <div class="mb-8">
    <span class="mb-2 block t-label">01 / ABOUT</span>
    <h1
      class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl"
      style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif;"
    >
      About me
    </h1>
  </div>

  <!-- Two-column layout on lg+: constrained prose left, photos right -->
  <div class="grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_auto] lg:gap-16">
    <!-- Left: prose column, capped at ~70ch -->
    <div class="min-w-0">
      <!-- Background -->
      <section class="mb-10" aria-labelledby="background-heading">
        <h2
          id="background-heading"
          class="mb-4 flex items-baseline gap-3 text-lg font-semibold"
          style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif;"
        >
          <span class="t-label">02 /</span> Background
        </h2>
        <div class="app-prose max-w-[70ch]">
          <p>
            I'm <strong>Jasper Japp</strong>, an Engineering (Honours) graduate
            from the <strong>Australian National University</strong> where I majored
            in
            <strong>Electronic &amp; Communication Systems</strong> with a minor
            in
            <strong>Mechatronic Systems</strong>. I've spent the last few years
            working and learning about aerodynamics, composite structures,
            embedded systems, and applied machine learning. What I enjoy most is
            finding a problem, learning what I can, and working towards a great
            solution. This is made even better when I get to do it with others.
            I think you'll find glimpses of that here, but it's by no means an
            exhaustive portfolio (but I'll do my best to update it once in a
            while).
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- What I've been working on -->
      <section class="mb-10" aria-labelledby="work-heading">
        <h2
          id="work-heading"
          class="mb-4 flex items-baseline gap-3 text-lg font-semibold"
          style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif;"
        >
          <span class="t-label">03 /</span> What I've been working on
        </h2>
        <div class="app-prose max-w-[70ch]">
          <p>
            Have a look around, but here's a real brief snapshot in a few
            sentences.
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <strong
                ><a href="/projects/solar-car-aero/"
                  >Solar car aerodynamics and structures:</a
                ></strong
              > Shaped a low-drag catamaran body, automated CFD runs with Python,
              and manufactured a carbon-fibre car. Optimised the structural layout
              to integrate electrical and mechanical systems seamlessly.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Mechanical design for solar racing:</strong> Designed four-bar
              linkage systems for <a href="/projects/fourbar-egress/"
                >driver egress</a
              > and <a href="/projects/solar-hinging/">solar array tilting</a>,
              balancing stiffness, packaging, and regulatory requirements.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong
                ><a href="/projects/bushfire-detection/"
                  >Early bushfire detection:</a
                ></strong
              > Built machine learning pipelines (GRU/GMM-VAE and STFT-CNN variants)
              to detect fires from IoT sensor data, with a focus on reducing false
              positives.
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            Lots of what I'm most proud of came from my time with ANU Solar
            Racing (most of the projects are things I did on my 2nd iteration
            with the team). New to Solar Racing? Read <a href="/solar-racing/"
              >What is Solar Racing?</a
            >
            for a quick overview and some more gorgeous shots of this very special
            car.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Outside of Engineering -->
      <section class="mb-10" aria-labelledby="outside-heading">
        <h2
          id="outside-heading"
          class="mb-4 flex items-baseline gap-3 text-lg font-semibold"
          style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif;"
        >
          <span class="t-label">04 /</span> Outside of Engineering
        </h2>
        <div class="app-prose max-w-[70ch]">
          <p>
            I feel as though I have an almost endless stream of hobbies. I love
            pulling a great shot of espresso. Skiing is one of my favourite
            things when I can get to the mountains. Been experimenting with some
            film photography. And I've started swimming to stay fit. I also
            always have a few projects on the go to keep me busy whether it's
            this website or something to help me learn.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- CV download -->
      <div class="mt-2">
        <a
          href="/JasperJapp_CV.pdf"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg border border-accent/40 bg-accent/5 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-accent no-underline glow-accent transition-colors hover:border-accent/70 hover:bg-accent/10 focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-accent focus-visible:outline-dashed"
          style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif;"
        >
          View CV
          <span class="t-label">PDF ↗</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Right: photos (stacks on mobile, right column on lg+) -->
    <aside
      class="flex flex-col gap-6 sm:flex-row sm:gap-6 lg:w-72 lg:flex-col xl:w-80"
      aria-label="Photos"
    >
      <!-- Photo 1 -->
      <figure class="group relative m-0 flex-1 lg:flex-none">
        <div
          class="overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-border transition-all duration-300 group-hover:border-accent/40"
          style="aspect-ratio: 3/2;"
        >
          <img
            src="/images/me/Profile.jpg"
            alt="Profile Picture"
            class="h-full w-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-[1.02]"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
          />
        </div>
        <figcaption class="mt-2 flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="t-label">FIG.01</span>
          <span class="t-label opacity-60">Profile</span>
        </figcaption>
      </figure>

      <!-- Photo 2: slightly offset on lg+ via margin-top -->
      <figure class="group relative m-0 flex-1 lg:mt-8 lg:flex-none">
        <div
          class="overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-border transition-all duration-300 group-hover:border-accent/40"
          style="aspect-ratio: 3/2;"
        >
          <img
            src="/images/me/speaking.jpg"
            alt="Presenting the solar car"
            class="h-full w-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-[1.02]"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
          />
        </div>
        <figcaption class="mt-2 flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="t-label">FIG.02</span>
          <span class="t-label opacity-60">Presenting the solar car</span>
        </figcaption>
      </figure>

      <!-- Status card fills the rail below the photos on lg+ -->
      <div
        class="relative card-hover p-5 before:absolute before:top-2.5 before:left-2.5 before:h-2 before:w-2 before:border-t before:border-l before:border-accent/30 after:absolute after:right-2.5 after:bottom-2.5 after:h-2 after:w-2 after:border-r after:border-b after:border-accent/30 sm:flex-1 lg:mt-8 lg:flex-none"
        data-animate
      >
        <span class="mb-3 block t-label">STATUS //</span>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-foreground/85">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-0.5 shrink-0 t-label">LOC</span>
            <span>Based in Sydney, Australia</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-0.5 shrink-0 t-label">ROLE</span>
            <span>Engineering Specialist at AirTrunk, since May 2026</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-0.5 shrink-0 t-label">WIP</span>
            <span
              >Working on a compact wireless communications project when it
              works</span
            >
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>
</Layout>

<script>
  // Scroll-reveal for data-animate elements
  const observer = new IntersectionObserver(
    entries => {
      entries.forEach(e => {
        if (e.isIntersecting) {
          e.target.classList.add("is-visible");
          observer.unobserve(e.target);
        }
      });
    },
    { threshold: 0.1 }
  );
  document
    .querySelectorAll("[data-animate]")
    .forEach(el => observer.observe(el));
  document.addEventListener("astro:after-swap", () => {
    document
      .querySelectorAll("[data-animate]")
      .forEach(el => observer.observe(el));
  });
</script>
